    "The development of definitions and methods to model and guarantee security for FHE schemes is currently an active area of research, and is beyond the scope of this paper.",
    "Hence, in this work we mainly focus on providing (computational) IND-CPA security for FHE.",
    "We leave the consideration of advanced security notions for future work.",
    "In this section we state the security levels that the parameter sets in Section 5.1 target, and we outline the assumptions under which we give estimates for the concrete security of those parameter sets.",
    "6 We use the notation s here to distinguish from the computational security parameter λ that is used elsewhere in the paper."
